=== Mental Health Crisis

Adolescents with severe ME/CFS are at increased risk for depression and suicidal ideation due to:

    - Loss of functional life, identity, and social connections
    - Chronic pain and suffering
    - Hopelessness about recovery
    - Feeling disbelieved by healthcare providers

